&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7572&quot; data-local-id=&quot;3d323e2e5b9d&quot;&gt;The focus of our team is our flagship product – the Carrier Store. This is the first touchpoint for independent agents on our platform, designed to make discovering and accessing insurance carriers seamless and highly personalized. We don’t believe in blind matching; our platform handles detailed vetting forms, and uses smart recommendation algorithms to connect them with the right partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;7968&quot; data-local-id=&quot;23fa58950bf8&quot;&gt;As a Senior Backend Engineer in this role, you will own the vetting, and access automation. This is a heavy, core backend domain where quality is non-negotiable and you cannot afford to make mistakes. You will work on critical funnel systems—like our Discovery path—which operates under heavy load.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;8268&quot; data-local-id=&quot;455cb07f195e&quot;&gt;If you thrive in a high-ownership environment with fast-paced priorities, heavy core logic, and continuous product discovery under heavy load – you’ve come to the right place. 🚀&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;What-You’ll-Do:&quot; data-local-id=&quot;3d40cc16ae12&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;8448&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/h3&gt;
