&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;8467&quot; data-local-id=&quot;a4f3a55577f5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Drive Access Automation &amp;amp; SSO:&lt;/strong&gt; You will implement SSO solutions and API integrations to overhaul manual carrier processes—scaling systems that currently rely on everything from raw APIs to carrier-managed Google Sheets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;8690&quot; data-local-id=&quot;17f96332276d&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Tackle Complex Challenges:&lt;/strong&gt; You will dive into deep architectural tasks, such as rebuilding licenses and access-sharing structures. This means doing the gritty, meticulous work of analyzing the legacy state, mapping out the target architecture, and executing it safely.&lt;/li&gt;
